## ğŸ’¡ Tips for Fact-Based Documentation

- âœ… Keep it short, clear, and objective.  
- âœ… Record the **reason for the call**, actions taken, and **outcome**.  
- âœ… Note frustration or urgency only in terms of the problem, e.g., â€œCustomer frustrated due to delayed shipment.â€  
- âœ… Use clear, professional language.  
